Package: MicroMeta
Title: meta-analysis version of Quasi-Conditional Association Tests for microbiome data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Shuren", "He", , email = "heshuren987@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A variety of meta-analysis methods for microbiome data, based on summary statistics generated by Quasi-Conditional Association Tests (QCAT) described in Tang Z.-Z. et al.(2017) <doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btw804>, including both fixed-effect meta-analysis methods like FE-SKAT test and Multivariate test and random effect meta-analysis methods such as Het-SKAT and RE-SKAT test described in Lee S. et al.(2013) <doi: 10.1016/j.ajhg.2013.05.010>.
